      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. It drives like a total dream and has been super reliable. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
