      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the S54B32 inline-six, the powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system for a linear power band and a sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and recently serviced rod bearings, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. The suspension retains its factory-correct damping rates, and the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering offers unfiltered feedback. A collector-grade specimen with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
