      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a mirror-finish exterior completely free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and crease-free, retaining that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, housing a powertrain that has been maintained with an open-checkbook policy and a full documented service history. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
